(89, 'widget_text', 'a:15:{i:6;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:8:"Facebook";s:4:"text";s:562:"<div style="height:210px;"><img src="http://1stsocial.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/Facebook.png" style="float:left; padding-right:5px;">Facebook is engaging, why would people interact with it so much if it wasn''t? We develop your presence through custom applications and enhanced interaction. Why settle for a static page when you can create an engaging environment for your brand? Engage more effectively on Facebook and watch your value proposition become socially viral!!</div>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.1stsocial.com.au/facebook-marketing/">READ MORE</a>\r\n";s:6:"filter";b:1;}i:7;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:7:"Twitter";s:4:"text";s:524:"<div style="height:210px;"><img src="http://1stsocial.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/Twitter-01.png" style="float:left; padding-right:5px;">Twitter allows you to reach a huge audience and we can tailor this reach to a global scale or local niche. Let us show you how to communicate with your cutting edge customers, clients and associates and in the process boost your brand recognition and increase traffic to your website and business.\r\n</div>\r\n<a href="http://www.1stsocial.com.au/twitter-marketing/">READ MORE</a>\r\n\r\n";s:6:"filter";b:1;}i:8;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:8:"About Us";s:4:"text";s:153:"1stSocial is a pioneering Social Media strategy development service offered by <a href="http://www.1stexecutive.com.au" target="_blank">1stExecutive</a>.";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:9;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"text";s:121:"<iframe width="263" height="163" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/gO9t_6Oofww" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:10;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:8:"LinkedIn";s:4:"text";s:398:"<div style="height:210px;"><img src="http://1stsocial.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/LinkedIn.png" style="float:left; padding-right:5px;" >LinkedIn has become the premiere social network for the business world. Let 1stSocial harness the power for your business and help you network with associates and clients.\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<a href="http://www.1stsocial.com.au/linkedin-marketing/">READ MORE</a>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:11;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:7:"YouTube";s:4:"text";s:435:"<div style="height:210px;"><img src="http://1stsocial.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/youtubeicon01.png" style="float:left; padding-right:5px;" >Not only will 1stSocial set up your business presence on YouTube and other video publishing websites such as Vimeo, but we can also film, edit and produce your video content.\r\n\r\nWhatever your video needs.\r\n</div>\r\n<a href="http://www.1stsocial.com.au/youtube-marketing/">READ MORE</a>\r\n\r\n";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:12;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:15:"About 1stSocial";s:4:"text";s:58:"1stSocial is a Melbourne based Social Media strategy firm.";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:13;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:12:"Testimonials";s:4:"text";s:15:""Blah blah bah"";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:14;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:18:"Facebook Marketing";s:4:"text";s:470:"<div style="height:210px;"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/facebookmarketing.jpg" style="float:left; padding-right:5px;">Facebook Marketing is more than just setting up a page and printing your URL on your business card. We keep your audience engaged through custom applications and interaction and develop unique product and content delivery systems. Oh, and everything we do is viral!</div>\r\n<a href="http://www.1stsocial.com.au/contact-us/">CONTACT US TODAY</a>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:15;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:21:"Facebook Recruitment ";s:4:"text";s:535:"<div style="height:210px;"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/facebookrecruitment.jpg" style="float:left; padding-right:5px;">With so many people on Facebook, is it any wonder that it is a great source for potential recruitment candidates? Many companies simply "push" job ads to their Facebook timeline, but these get lost in the sea of status updates. Instead, let us set up a fully viral job delivery application your candidates and clients will love!</div>\r\n<a href="http://www.1stsocial.com.au/contact-us/">CONTACT US TODAY</a>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:16;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:12:"Set it & Go!";s:4:"text";s:896:"<div style="height:210px;"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/setitandgo.jpg" style="float:left; padding-right:5px;">We understand that you''ve got a business to run, and maintaining your Social Media isn''t it. That''s why we automate every process possible, and link all of your <a href="http://www.1stsocial.com.au/social-networks/">Social Network</a> together. That means your <a href="http://www.1stsocial.com.au/facebook-marketing/">Facebook</a>, <a href="http://www.1stsocial.com.au/twitter-marketing/">Twitter</a>, <a href="http://www.1stsocial.com.au/linkedin-marketing/">LinkedIn</a>, <a href="http://www.1stsocial.com.au/youtube-marketing/">Youtube</a>, website and more all work automatically to keep each other updated! It''s like a whole team that works for you, leaving you time to focus on other things.</div>\r\n<a href="http://www.1stsocial.com.au/contact-us/">CONTACT US TODAY</a>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:17;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:10:"Contact Us";s:4:"text";s:105:"<div style="height:210px;"><a href="http://www.1stsocial.com.au/contact-us/">CONTACT US TODAY</a></div>\r\n";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:19;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:19:"Twitter Recruitment";s:4:"text";s:432:"<div style="height:210px;"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/facebookrecruitment.jpg" style="float:left; padding-right:5px;">\r\nWith so many people on Twitter, not only is it a great source of candidates, but also an important tool when publishing your job vacancies. We can use hashtags to target specific demographics and engage them where they are!</div>\r\n<a href="http://www.1stsocial.com.au/contact-us/">CONTACT US TODAY</a>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:20;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:17:"Twitter Marketing";s:4:"text";s:540:"<div style="height:210px;"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/facebookmarketing.jpg" style="float:left; padding-right:5px;">\r\nWe''ll create you a custom company profile, give you the tools you need to engage with other users, and automatically publish relevant content so that your profile, and thus business, can be seen as a Leader. We''ll target your demographic, no matter how big or small, and engage them with information about your products and services.</div>\r\n<a href="http://www.1stsocial.com.au/contact-us/">CONTACT US TODAY</a>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}s:12:"_multiwidget";i:1;}', 'yes'),
