(6, 1, '2012-08-02 06:07:22', '2012-08-02 06:07:22', '<a href="http://www.mri-scan.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/ProfitFromIT2-300x249.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-11" title="ProfitFromIT2-300x249" src="http://www.mri-scan.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/ProfitFromIT2-300x249.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="249" /></a>You know how CIO’s, CFO’s and CEO’s are constantly under pressure to upgrade systems, acquire new software and invest in the latest technology? Well, what we do is respond to your business’s competitive pressure and find ways for you to profit from the IT you have already got.\r\n\r\nWe have saved companies who run mission critical systems hundreds of thousands of dollars and also improved IT productivity on the simple premise that systems, software and resources, however old or however “critical," are usually asked to do less than they are capable of.\r\n\r\nMRI-Scan is a truly independent IT Audit that looks at all aspects of your IT operation and saves you money. We will also identify, with complete independence, what is best for your business.\r\n\r\nWe understand that while vendors have the pressure on to keep upgrading, it is the customer and internal pressure to reduce costs and increase efficiencies that are most keenly felt.  This is where an IT audit from MRI-Scan will pay dividends.\r\n\r\nWith the technology world moving so quickly, it is often existing systems and relationships that are often overlooked. IT is an area which often avoids real scrutiny, and has an air of ''mystery''. We know that often C level executives want simple solutions but receive complex answers. Even by completing a simple IT audit, there can be massive savings found with no change to any environment or vendor.\r\n\r\nOur solution to help you profit from IT is to provide a truly independent IT audit of your current situation, we even prefer to have the majority of our fees tied to the savings we realize – so you can reward results – after all, isn’t that how your business is paid?\r\n\r\nThis is all done through a patented process that can help you re-repatriate profits from IT to enhance and drive your business growth.', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2012-08-02 06:22:58', '2012-08-02 06:22:58', '', 0, 'http://mri-scan.com.au/?page_id=6', 0, 'page', '', 0),
